_json.gridTitle: All the Ways You Can Style the Maxwell Sofa
_json.description: When shopping for a sofa, versatility and durability are probably the two most important factors you’re looking for—after all, sofas are a major investment, in terms of both physical space and budget. When you find one that ticks all the boxes, you want to tell everyone—which is why we’re telling you about the Maxwell Sofa from Interior Define, designed by our very own Founder & CEO Maxwell Ryan.Maybe we’re a little biased, but this sofa is pretty much perfect.
